Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:47.30,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,CRING!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:51.60,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,LESU
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:52.22,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,CRING!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:40.15,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,JRENG!
